        <mxCell id="wz-agent" value="&lt;b&gt;wazuh-agent DaemonSet&lt;/b&gt; (custom image: wazuh-agent-local:4.14.1)&#10;hostNetwork • hostPID • cluster-admin SA&#10;reads /host/var/run/cilium/tetragon/tetragon.log → forwards to wazuh-workers:1514&#10;active-response: delete-pod.py (in-cluster k8s API)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe0b2;strokeColor=#ef6c00;fontSize=10" vertex="1" parent="1">
